{"id":"h_mr6a1h0g_h2e5vgie","text":"When fanning out read-only reviewers in parallel with a mutating tester over shared state files, warn EVERY reader about transient mutations (or sequence them) — otherwise reviewers report probe-injected state as live findings.","scope":"project","project":"/Users/harissaif/.pi/agent","category":"orchestration","created":"2026-07-04T11:26:35.104Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-04T11:26:35.104Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false,"basis":"directly-observed"}
{"id":"h_mr6dboka_uy65zqs8","text":"graphify-out/ is in .gitignore but files committed before the rule (graph.json, manifest.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md, graph.html, dated snapshots) remain tracked and churn porcelain/auto-commits on every rebuild — treat those M entries as ambient, and don't trust the \"graphify-out is gitignored\" doc claim for tracked paths.","scope":"project","project":"/Users/harissaif/.pi/agent","category":"gotcha","created":"2026-07-04T12:58:30.298Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-04T12:58:30.298Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false,"basis":"directly-observed"}
{"id":"h_mr6dbon1_h1zgzd1g","text":"Extension messages sent with deliverAs:\"nextTurn\" (graph-first nudge, impact-trace) are invisible to the agent within the same run — verify those branches behaviorally (e.g. the 2nd structure grep blocking proves the 1st nudged) or by jiti-loading the extension with a stub pi that records sendMessage.","scope":"project","project":"/Users/harissaif/.pi/agent","category":"gotcha","created":"2026-07-04T12:58:30.397Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-04T12:58:30.397Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false,"basis":"reproduced"}
{"id":"h_mr6iixd1_fugtabzo","text":"In ~/.pi/agent's graphify graph, ~41% of nodes are the vendored git/github.com/DietrichGebert/ponytail repo whose only bridge to the config-repo is a shared `path` import, so a FULL code re-extraction (/graph update or bare graphify) can detach it and drop the giant-component fraction to ~0.48, re-tripping the audit-pipelines ratchet even from a healthy graph — restore from graphify-out/<date>/ an","scope":"project","project":"/Users/harissaif/.pi/agent","category":"gotcha","created":"2026-07-04T15:24:06.372Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-04T15:24:06.372Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false,"basis":"reproduced"}
